name: Quick Reflexes
Lore: 'Boba Fett''s helmet has infrared capabilities, a motion tracking system, a macrobinocular viewer, an internal comlink and a broadband antenna. He doesn''t miss a thing.',
Text: 'Deploy on your side of table. During your draw phase, you make use 2 Force to search through your Lost Pile. Take one Hidden Weapons into hand or take any one blaster and immediately deploy it (for free).',
